{"fadeType":1,"id":"SANLI09","mode":2,"scripts":[{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"三笠大先輩、昨日の宴会はどうもありがとうございました。…でも大先輩が言ってたこと、私にはまだちょっとよく分からなくて……","actor":307060,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":2},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"なら、我と一回演習で勝負でもしてみるか？","dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":305110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"三笠大先輩と…ですか？","actor":307060,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"うむ。切磋琢磨は重要だ。何かがひらめくかも知れぬぞ。","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"はい！全力で行かせていただきます！演習海域はちょうど空いていますから、三笠大先輩、今から行きましょう！","actor":307060,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"我はここでも構わぬが……まあ良い。では演習海域に出航しよう。って瑞鶴、ちょっと待てーー","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"（あの時、ダンスは苦手だと言ったのに、我の足を一回も踏まなかったな……）","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"say":"一刻後"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"瑞鶴！セイレーンとの戦いでの勢いはどうした！","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"攻撃が全てわざとらしすぎる！どこを狙っているかひと目でわかるぞ！","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"やっぱり、大先輩には勝てない……か……","actor":307060,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"そんなことあるか！今のはお主の全力ではあるまい！","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"……兵装には問題ないはず、でもなぜ……大先輩相手にはやっぱり……","actor":307060,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"まだ気づいておらぬか。お主は我と戦う時、そしてセイレーン・エンタープライズと戦う時と比べて決定的な差があるーー","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"……？","actor":307060,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"我を傷つけるのを恐れるあまり、全ての攻撃前に躊躇しているのだ。","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"…戦いを単純に考えすぎる者もいるが、お主はその逆だ。戦闘に入ったら、余計なことを考えるな！","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"そう言われても……！","actor":307060,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"お主が気にすることもわかる。しかしだ、お主が自分の道を決めない限り、誰もがそれを決められまい。","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"我の後を追っかけるのも構わぬ。だが――「全てを賭ける」と決めているのなら、最後まで貫け！","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"私の、全て……わかりました。三笠大先輩！またいつかお手合わせお願いできませんか？","actor":307060,"dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"構わぬぞ。お主のためなら、我はその第一歩となろう。","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"…ただ、あまり長く待たせるでないぞ。その後はお主の努力が必要になるのだからな――","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"side":1,"say":"……","dir":-1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"blackBg":true},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"ふぅ……ここだな。","dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"actor":305110},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"この旗は、一体……？","actor":307050,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:95}","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"かつて我を勝利に導いた旗だ。","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"この旗さえあれば、お主らはきっと勝利への道を見つけ出せる。","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"威厳で敵勢を挫き、勇気で性能差を補い、信念と根性で最後の最後まで粘り勝つ。","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"かの時代でもここでも「奇跡」は起こりえぬ。だが「奇跡的な勝利」は確かにあるのだ。この旗は、我が信念とともに、お主に預けるとしよう！","actor":305110,"dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:82}","side":1}],"fadein":1.5,"fadeOut":1.5}